description: Are you interested in learning fun facts about your own species?  This Alexa skill helps you do just that!  Ask Alexa using sample phrases such as, "Alexa, ask human facts to tell me a human fact." or "Alexa, ask human facts to give me a human trivia."  Impress your friends with fun facts about us!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask human facts to tell me a human fact
Alexa, ask human facts to tell me human trivia
Alexa, ask human facts to give me a human trivia
name: HumanFacts
shortDescription: A skill set that tells you interesting facts about humans.
